data.description: With over 1,600 square feet this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is located in a nice, quiet neighborhood in Boaz. This home offers hardwood flooring along with an additional den and office space that could serve as a 4th bedroom. Also included is a 575 sq ft detached garage/shop building with fenced in back yard along with an additional .43 acre lot beside the property. Perfect home for the family. Possible Owner Financing available! Call to take a tour today
